{"tid":1914864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急重要] 為免俾黑警拎左張SIM 卡用，請大家要開SIM PIN Lock!","createTime":"2020-03-07T20:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T00:29:28.000Z","uid":14087,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"09a52de9cf7a9bd7bbe17eaf634036b0746b6217","tid":1914864,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T20:40:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>方法：設定 - 流動網絡 - SIM PIN - 選擇開啟 SIM PIN。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如你的手機<span style=\"color: red;\"> SIM 卡沒有上鎖</span>，萬一有人檢獲你的手機，即使你的手機本身有密碼，但<span style=\"color: red;\">匪徒(黑警)只需要把 SIM 卡取出</span>，就能<span style=\"color: red;\">接收訊息</span>。若然你主要的<span style=\"color: red;\">通訊軟件或社交媒體帳號，都是綁定了該手機號碼，而你又從來沒有設置過雙重認證，匪徒就能輕易而舉，用你的手機接收一個六位數字的驗證短訊，</span>並登入你的<span style=\"color: red;\"> WhatsApp</span>。更甚者也可以重設<span style=\"color: red;\">社交媒體或電郵帳號的登入密碼，冒充你的名字發送訊息</span>（最理想是避免一個手機號碼就能重設帳戶號碼，但有機會另文再談）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E4%B8%80-sim-%E5%8D%A1%E9%8E%96/?fbclid=IwAR2p1UP3fEjXzfx9muFPUtc3qVS8E_dye73PTZgGEP70aMDbyZkuT2mNfS8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E4%25B8%2580-sim-%25E5%258D%25A1%25E9%258E%2596%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2p1UP3fEjXzfx9muFPUtc3qVS8E_dye73PTZgGEP70aMDbyZkuT2mNfS8&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=592e2a89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E4%25B8%2580-sim-%25E5%258D%25A1%25E9%258E%2596%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2p1UP3fEjXzfx9muFPUtc3qVS8E_dye73PTZgGEP70aMDbyZkuT2mNfS8&h=26da3c40\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F